info.author: Michael Dunlap
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.name: Products.PloneKeywordManager
info.summary: Plone Keyword Manager allows you to change, merge and delete keywords in Plone and updates all corresponding objects automatically. It uses a similiarity search to support you in identifying similar keywords. Keywords can be cleaned up from time to time by a site manager to create a consistent vocabulary.
